name: createVoucherEntryAndEdit

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to Voucher Entry page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Voucher Entries,Voucher Entry}

testSteps.description: Then the Payment Information form and its contents should show up
When I set the Supplier to '118173'
When I set the 'Invoice Number' to 'I9pLV1Ilwz'
When I set the Currency to 'USD'
When i click on continue button
When I select the first Bank Account and click 'Submit' button if modal exist
When I set the Gross Amount to '10000'
When i click on continue button
Then the 'GL Distribution' form and its contents should show up
When I set the Account Number to '91100'
When I set the Line Description to 'Test'
When I set the Amount to '10000'
When I set the Employee to 'Milos Vitas'
When I set the Cost Center to '1MAN400'
When I set the General Obj to 'AFGHAI'
When I click on the 'Show Next' button
When I set the AOE to 'YAO'
When I set the Line Ref to 'Test123'
When I set the Purchase Order to '12345'
When I set the Units to '10'
When I set the Unit of Measure to '10'
When I click on 'Save' button
Then the voucher entry successfully created modal and its contents should show up

children.description: Then the voucher entry successfully created modal should show up
Then the batch number from voucher entry successfully created modal should show up
Then the document number from voucher entry successfully created modal should show up

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged into 'Voucher Entry Review' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Review A/P Entries,Voucher Entries}

testSteps.description: Then the 'Voucher Entry Review' page and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Batch Number' using saved value
When I click on 'Search' button
Then the 'Review Voucher' search result should show up
When I select the first voucher entry
When I click on 'Edit' button
When I click 'Payment Amount' button
Then the 'Payment Amount' form should show up
When I set the Gross Amount to '1500'
When I click on 'Continue' button
Then the 'GL Distribution' form should show up
When I set the Account Number to '212100'
When I set the Amount to '1500'
When I set the Cost Center to 'KYI2100'
When I click on 'Save' button
Then the voucher entry successfully created modal and its contents should show up

children.description: Then the voucher entry successfully created modal should show up

children.description: Then the batch number from voucher entry successfully created modal should show up
Then the document number from voucher entry successfully created modal should show up

testSteps.description: When i click on modal review button
When I select the first voucher entry
When I click on 'View Entries' button
Then the 'Voucher Entry' modal should show up
Then the Cost center of the first voucher entry in Voucher Entry modal should be set to 'KYI2100'
Then the Account Number of the first voucher entry in Voucher Entry modal should be set to '212100'
Then the Amount of the first voucher entry in Voucher Entry modal should be set to '1500'
When i close the modal
